Bumpmap (Material global keyword)
=================================

Description
-----------

Creates a [Texturing.html\#Bump\_maps bump map] stage in a material shader.

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

`bumpmap [map]`

Parameters
----------

-   [map] - the relative path and file name from /[Base\_(folder).html base] to the specified bump map image.

Notes
-----

This keyword is shorthand for...

`{`
` blend bumpmap`
` map [map]`
`}`


